Troika’s Greece Statement to Suggest Payment of Loan, Vima Says

-- B y   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 
2011-10-11T10:54:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/troika-s-greece-statement-to-suggest-payment-of-loan-vima-says.html
The European Union,  International
Monetary Fund  and European Central Bank team of inspectors of
 Greece ’s economic progress will indicate in a statement today
that the sixth loan should be paid, To Vima newspaper reported,
without citing anyone.  The statement from the so-called troika will criticise
Greece for the slow pace of reforms and will note how budget
targets have been missed because of the deeper than forecast
contraction of the economy, the Athens-based newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
